name: gruvbox syntax highlighting
description:
This community Figma file is an unofficial recreation of the palette images from the gruvbox readme:
https://github.com/morhetz/gruvbox#readme

Gruvbox is a code syntax highlighting theme.

This file contains all defined colors from the palette, so you can use it as a library.

I originally created this for a unique webpage design in a style that's supposed to look similar to what programmers see when editing code.
